-> Flask: The web framework.

-> Flask-SQLAlchemy: ORM integration for Flask.

-> Flask-Migrate: Database migrations.

-> Flask-WTF: Form handling and CSRF protection.

-> Flask-Login: User session management.

-> Werkzeug[bcrypt]: For password hashing (installed by Werkzeug as bcrypt is a dependency for the password utilities).

p-> ython-dotenv: For loading environment variables.

Project Structure (Initial):

event_management_system/
├── venv/
├── .env                  # Environment variables
├── requirements.txt      # Project dependencies
├── run.py                # Script to run the application
└── app/                  # Main application package
    ├── __init__.py       # App creation and configuration
    ├── config.py         # Configuration settings
    ├── models.py         # Database models
    ├── forms.py          # WTForms definitions
    ├── routes.py         # Route definitions (initially, later split into blueprints)
    ├── templates/        # HTML templates
    │   └── base.html
    │   └── home.html
    └── static/           # Static files (CSS, JS, images)
        └── css/
        └── js/
